---
const links = [
  { label: 'About', href: '/company/about' },
  { label: 'Security', href: '/company/security' },
  { label: 'Contact', href: '/company/contact' },
  { label: 'Privacy', href: '/legal/privacy' },
  { label: 'Terms', href: '/legal/terms' }
];
---
<section class="bg-ink text-paper">
  <div class="container-wide py-20">
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow text-paper/70">Next step</div>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-[clamp(2.2rem,4.6vw,3.75rem)] font-semibold tracking-tight text-paper">
          Are you ready to transform your brand?
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-[80ch] text-lg leading-relaxed text-paper/80 md:text-xl">
          Share your thoughts about what you’re building, where AI engages with your brand, and what needs
          controlling. We can help you clarify and scope your next steps.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <a
          href="#get-in-touch"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-strandGreen px-8 py-4 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-ink shadow-outline hover:bg-strandGreen/90 transition-colors"
        >
          Get in touch
        </a>
        <a
          href="/use-cases"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-paper/20 bg-transparent px-8 py-4 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-paper hover:border-paper/40 transition-colors"
        >
          View use cases
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section
  id="get-in-touch"
  class="bg-[url('/images/get-in-touch/bgimage.webp')] bg-cover bg-center"
>
  <div>
    <div class="container-wide py-24">
      <div class="grid overflow-hidden shadow-outline lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr]">
        <div class="relative min-h-[440px] overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10 h-full">
            <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 bg-strandGreen">
              <div class="m-8 max-w-[360px] px-10 pb-6 text-ink">
                <div class="text-8xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
                  Get in touch.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-paper p-12 lg:-mr-[calc(50vw-50%)] lg:pr-[calc(50vw-50%)]">
          <form id="home-contact-form" class="grid gap-6 max-w-[520px]" novalidate>
            <div class="grid gap-2">
              <label for="home-name" class="text-base font-semibold text-ink/70">Name</label>
              <input
                id="home-name"
                name="name"
                type="text"
                autocomplete="name"
                required
                class="border-b border-fog bg-transparent pb-3 text-base text-ink outline-none focus:border-ink"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="grid gap-2">
              <label for="home-email" class="text-base font-semibold text-ink/70">Email*</label>
              <input
                id="home-email"
                name="email"
                type="email"
                autocomplete="email"
                inputmode="email"
                required
                class="border-b border-fog bg-transparent pb-3 text-base text-ink outline-none focus:border-ink"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="grid gap-2">
              <label for="home-subject" class="text-base font-semibold text-ink/70">Subject*</label>
              <input
                id="home-subject"
                name="topic"
                type="text"
                required
                class="border-b border-fog bg-transparent pb-3 text-base text-ink outline-none focus:border-ink"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="grid gap-2">
              <label for="home-message" class="text-base font-semibold text-ink/70">Message</label>
              <textarea
                id="home-message"
                name="message"
                rows="4"
                required
                class="border-b border-fog bg-transparent pb-3 text-base text-ink outline-none focus:border-ink"
              ></textarea>
            </div>

              <div class="pt-2">
                <div class="flex justify-end pr-10">
                  <button
                    type="submit"
                    class="rounded-md bg-ink px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-paper"
                  >
                    Submit
                  </button>
                </div>
                <div id="home-contact-status" class="mt-3 text-sm text-steel" aria-live="polite"></div>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate text-paper">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container-wide relative z-10 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[980px]">
      <img
        src="/images/partners/advanced-analytica.svg"
        alt="Advanced Analytica"
        loading="lazy"
        class="mx-auto h-10 w-auto opacity-90 md:h-12"
      />

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-paper/85 md:text-lg">
        <p>
          To succeed today, business must respond to challenges that are not addressed by traditional approaches.
          They require world-class solutions that integrate people, processes, information and technology at the time
          they are needed.
        </p>
        <p>
          Advanced Analytica partners with these businesses to protect and capitalise on data and AI, manage risk,
          deliver transparency and control costs. Through enterprise-level expertise and three decades of deep
          industry experience, Advanced Analytica creates real value through the use of innovative technology and
          intelligent automation that turns data into a strategic asset.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <div class="text-lg text-paper/80">Supported by</div>
        <img
          src="/images/partners/innovate-uk-edge.svg"
          alt="UKRI, Innovate UK, Business Connect"
          loading="lazy"
          class="mx-auto mt-7 h-10 w-auto opacity-90 md:h-12"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="border-t border-paper/10 bg-ink text-paper">
  <div class="container-wide flex flex-col gap-6 py-10 text-sm text-paper/70">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <div class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-paper">Brand Semantics</div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        {links.map((item) => (
          <a href={item.href} class="hover:text-paper transition-colors">{item.label}</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-xs">© {new Date().getFullYear()} Brand Semantics. Built for static deployment.</div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script is:inline>
  (() => {
    const form = document.getElementById("home-contact-form");
    const status = document.getElementById("home-contact-status");
    if (!form) return;

    const setStatus = (msg) => {
      if (status) status.textContent = msg;
    };

    form.addEventListener("submit", (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();

      const fd = new FormData(form);
      const name = String(fd.get("name") || "").trim();
      const email = String(fd.get("email") || "").trim();
      const topic = String(fd.get("topic") || "").trim();
      const message = String(fd.get("message") || "").trim();

      if (!name || !email || !topic || !message) {
        setStatus("Please complete the required fields.");
        return;
      }

      const subject = `Brand Semantics briefing request: ${topic}`;
      const body = [
        `Name: ${name}`,
        `Email: ${email}`,
        `Topic: ${topic}`,
        "",
        "---",
        "",
        message
      ]
        .filter(Boolean)
        .join("\n");

      const mailto = `mailto:?subject=${encodeURIComponent(subject)}&body=${encodeURIComponent(body)}`;

      setStatus("Opening email draft…");
      window.location.href = mailto;
    });
  })();
</script>
